Package com.cafean.client.mdocs

Class ALDocReferenceTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.mdocs.ALDocReferenceTable
  • public class ALDocReferenceTable
extends java.lang.Object
    A reference table intended to be used to organize notes based on the components that refer to them and the sub-systems containing those components.
